> P160 is a multi-biometric time, attendance and access control identification station, which can connect to a third-party electric lock, door sensor, exit button, etc.

Using the latest Palm / fingerprint identification algorithm and simplified technology, it can contain 1000 Palm templates and up to 3000 fingerprint templates without dividing into groups.

Connecting via Wi-Fi, TCP / IP and USB host, it ensures a smooth connection and data transfer. The incredible verification speed and intuitive operation process make it popular.

Elaborately designed and precisely processed, it perfectly matches your slap desk.
